create a new jon select pipline

2: Configure the Pipeline
Scroll down to the Pipeline section.
Set Definition to “Pipeline script from SCM”.
Choose SCM as Git.
In Repository URL, enter: use 

Branch, enter:main


In Script Path, enter:jenkinsfile

-----------------------------------------
Add Maven in Jenkins
Go to Jenkins Dashboard → Manage Jenkins → Global Tool Configuration.

Scroll to Maven section.
click Add Maven.

Set:
Name: maven 3.9.10

In the same Global Tool Configuration page, scroll to JDK section.

Click Add JDK.

Set:Name: openjdk 21.0.7

enter same version everywhere
